= AndStatus =

AndStatus is a low traffic social networking client with tree-like threaded conversations.
It supports multiple protocols, including [http://gnu.io/social/ GNU social] ([http://status.net/ StatusNet], e.g. [https://quitter.se/ Quitter], [https://loadaverage.org/ LoadAverage], [https://status.vinilox.eu/ Vinilox], etc.), [https://twitter.com Twitter] and [http://pump.io Pump.io].
AndStatus combines your accounts from all networks into one Timeline and allows you to read and post even while you are offline.

For Android OS version 4.1 or higher.
Under Free/Libre and Open Source License.

For more information please read the [https://github.com/andstatus/andstatus/wiki AndStatus Wiki]. 

